      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width\" id=\"faq\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-title\">よくある質問</h2>\n  <div class=\"faq-container\">\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          予約フォーム記入で予約とみなされますか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <!-- 横棒 -->\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <!-- 縦棒 -->\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        担当から別途申込書が送られてきますので、そちらの記入をもって予約完了となります。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          予約商品の支払いはいつ頃ですか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        10月14日以降にご入金方法をご連絡いたします。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          発送はいつ頃ですか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        ご入金確認後に製造を開始し、約6～12週間後の発送となります。生産状況で遅延が生じる場合は事前にご連絡いたします。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          請求書払いはできますか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        可能です。その場合は予約フォーム記入後にメールにてご連絡を差し上げる担当へとご相談をお願いいたします。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          領収書は発行されますか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        発行可能です。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          適格事業者ですか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        適格事業者番号を取得しております。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"faq-question\">\n        <div class=\"faq-question-text\">\n          <span class=\"faq-icon\">Q</span>\n          実物をみることはできますか？\n        </div>\n        <svg class=\"toggle-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 36 36\">\n          <path class=\"bar-horizontal\" d=\"M9 18.5h18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n          <path class=\"bar-vertical\" d=\"M18.5 9v18\" stroke=\"#8B6B3F\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        <span class=\"faq-icon\">A：</span>\n        2025年日本国際博覧会（大阪・関西万博）の「日本政府館」にて、「藻類スツール」を展示しております。なお、会場に展示されているスツールの座面にある日本館のロゴマークは、販売品には含まれませんのでご了承ください。\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"contact\" id=\"contact\">\n    <h2 class=\"contact-title\">製品に関する<br class=\"sp-br\">お問い合わせ相談</h2>\n    <p>通常３営業日以内に返信します。</p>\n    <a href=\"#\">問い合わせフォーム</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.faq-title {\n  font-size: 28px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n  text-align: center;\n  color: #FFF;\n}\n.faq-container {\n  margin-inline: 20rem;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 2rem;\n}\n.faq-item {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 1px;\n}\n.faq-question {\n  width: 100%;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  background: #FFFFFF;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  padding: 2px 0 2px 15px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  color: #8B6B3F;\n}\n.faq-question:hover {\n  opacity: 0.5;\n}\n.faq-icon {\n}\n.toggle-icon {\n  width: 36px;\n  height: 36px;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  display: block;\n}\n.bar-vertical {\n  transition: opacity 0.3s;\n}\n.faq-item.active .bar-vertical {\n  opacity: 0; /* 開いたときは縦棒を非表示にして－に */\n}\n.faq-answer {\n  display: none;\n  background: #fff;\n  padding: 15px;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  color: #8B6B3F;\n}\n.faq-item.active .faq-answer {\n  display: block;\n}\n.contact {\n  margin-top: 5rem;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.contact .contact-title {\n  font-size: 28px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n  text-align: center;\n  color: #FFF;\n  margin: 0 0 1rem;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n.contact p {\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: #FFF;\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n.contact a {\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin-top: 1rem;\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  background-color: #FFFFFF;\n  color: #8B6B3F;\n  text-decoration: none;\n}\n@media screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n\t.faq-container {\n\t\tmargin-inline: 2rem;\n\t}\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n  const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll(\".faq-item\");\n  faqItems.forEach(item => {\n    item.querySelector(\".faq-question\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(e) {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      item.classList.toggle(\"active\");\n    });\n  });\n});\n</script>",
